{"tid":947068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大陸化】香港碰瓷黨四度出手圖屈司機　警拘一男一女","createTime":"2018-12-19T03:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T04:00:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fbdd6faa2ea9eaf46dee53ef0daf89001482a5","tid":947068,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/CRASH-02_RE6By_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FCRASH-02_RE6By_1200x0.png&h=a557734b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網絡片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n在內地常出現的碰瓷黨，有本地港人效法。警方拘捕一男一女的本地人，懷疑他們與本月 8 日在長沙灣道發生的撞車黨案件有關，警方亦指該名男子涉及另外 3 宗在西九龍區發生同的類案件，不過並未成功詐騙金錢。<br />\n<br />\n網上有人上載一條車 cam 片段，顯示拍攝日期是本月 8 日；根據車 cam 畫面資訊，當時私家車以時速 16 公里沿長沙灣道往太子方向行駛。當駛過一個路口時，一名男子突然衝出馬路，被車撞到。但私家車司機認為男子刻意被撞，即時停車並下車理論，被撞男子清醒，自行站起來，並指自己只是「過馬路」。<br />\n<br />\n調查案件的深水埗警區刑事總督察呂雪琪表示，涉事報案的司機下車了解事件時，被撞男子和他發生爭執，當司機一報警，男子馬上離開，司機嘗試追截，但就被另一名女子阻礙，兩人最終逃脫。警方後來在案發兩日後以企圖欺詐罪拘捕二人，他們獲准保釋。警方經調查後發現，被捕男子涉嫌在去年至今年期間，在深水埗、旺角和油麻地涉及 3 宗同類案件，所以在昨日再拘捕他，男子目前仍被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n她指幾宗案件都沒有一些特定的地點發生，但都是在道路交界位置，而疑犯亦從未得逞，「當日以普通的交通意外案件去處理。他很快，警方一到場或未到場便離開了。每次金額都是數百元，未有案件是成功敲詐到車主。」呂雪琪指，另外 3 宗案的司機都有報警和拒絕賠償，暫時沒有證據顯示事件有集團操控，她又提醒司機，如果有安裝行車攝錄儀，可以防止同類罪案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1i9kWQLXQvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1i9kWQLXQvI&d=pvhBAVBnmSzUoSw0xFwVY1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=87ad1bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1i9kWQLXQvI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%8C%96-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A2%B0%E7%93%B7%E9%BB%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%BA%A6%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E5%9C%96%E5%B1%88%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%258C%2596-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A2%25B0%25E7%2593%25B7%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25B1%2588%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A5%25B3%2F&d=pvhBAVBnmSzUoSw0xFwVY1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=891c47eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%258C%2596-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A2%25B0%25E7%2593%25B7%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25B1%2588%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A5%25B3%2F&h=1c37d08e\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%8C%96-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A2%B0%E7%93%B7%E9%BB%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%BA%A6%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E5%9C%96%E5%B1%88%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3/</a>"},{"pid":"f46f5d3970f43f9efba1abcc60fd7637c5e8d764","tid":947068,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"撞車黨就撞車黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48666960a59ed0202704e52a8a3657140f48bf5f","tid":947068,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f46f5d3970f43f9efba1abcc60fd7637c5e8d764","tid":947068,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"撞車黨就撞車黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"以為係d大陸西屈鳩人整爛d瓷器"},{"pid":"6f380816535ee79f5faab023c38d80a3dca9dc1e","tid":947068,"uid":129739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"狂賀，香港變中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"